snippet.textDisplay:
Not sure if anyone noticed. there are three ladies in entire gang. Hats off to A R Rehman for encouraging newcomers.
I remember  Issrath used to tell me... back in early 2000s when Rehman would call her down to the studio ( studio used to be in Ground floor and home in the first) she would run excited thinking it is a chance to sing for him. But it will turn out to be get some water or tea or something. Now after so many years when I see her in a exclusive video, I am all tears. Go Girl!

snippet.textDisplay:
My humble effort to translate this profound song... who are you Kutti Revathi??
Within me shines a great light.
In the Sky floats (Tamil) music.
Any river  culminates  its course in my heart. What wonder!
In there I watched the Ocean swell 
I  realized  the Self,  Myself.
My face to realize its intellect, 
My "Dwelling" to realize its beauty.
I care not for "swayamvar"(seeking petty  things)
but for freedom.
I will adorn great capacity  and will dare (to achieve)
snippet.textOriginal:
